# if, else if, else

```javascript
if (age >= 18) {
    console.log("Voter");
} else {
    console.log("Minor");
}
```

# Switch-Case

Best for matching multiple specific values.

```javascript
switch(day) {
    case 1: console.log("Mon"); break;
    default: console.log("Invalid");
}
```

# Counting Loops

```javascript
for (let i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
    console.log(i);
}
```

# Writing Functions

```javascript
// Declaration
function add(a, b) { return a + b; }

// Expression
const sub = function(a, b) { return a - b; };
```

# Changing the Page

```javascript
btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
  document.body.style.background = 'red';
});
```

# Modern OOP

```javascript
class User {
  constructor(name) { this.name = name; }
  greet() { return `Hi ${this.name}`; }
}
```
